These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: r&b, trance, gospel, rock, jazz, punk, folk
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
4. the fan of jazz is between the fan of r&b and the fan of gospel##2
5. the fan of rock is between the fan of trance and the fan of r&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | folk | gospel | jazz | r&b | rock | trance | punk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, card-games, dancing, video-games, singing, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | singing | board-games | cooking | card-games | dancing | drawing | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: skydiving, chess, filmmaking, collecting, cooking, gardening, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | video-games | gardening | cooking | chess | skydiving | filmmaking | collecting |

